information: The company BLUMEN-KUNSTGEWERBE REICHERT MARTHA REICHERT INH. ANGELIKA FRITZ E.K., is a Retailer, founded in 1988, which operates in the Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry industry. It is based in Karlsruhe, Germany.
